<h3 class="text -help-title">Burning of Rice Straw</h3>
<p class="text -plain-text">
  The combustion of rice straw produces nitrous oxide emissions through
  direct emissions and leaching/run off but not through volatilization
  (cf IPCC 2006).
</p>
<p class="text -plain-text -note">
  Details on the methods used to calculate emissions from rice irrigation can
  be found at [Link to Methods doc].
</p>
